【ZD】工地项目采用 WebRTC 技术与安全帽语音摄像头进行交互，安全帽摄取的视频在火狐浏览器播放正常，在谷歌浏览器无法播放；

## 了解 WebRTC

>WebRTC (Web Real-Time Communications) 是一项实时通讯技术，它允许网络应用或者站点，在不借助中间媒介的情况下，建立浏览器之间点对点（Peer-to-Peer）的连接，实现视频流和（或）音频流或者其他任意数据的传输。从而降低延迟和带宽消耗

#### 浏览器支持情况
- Google Chrome 59
- Mozilla Firefox 54
- Opera 18
- Safari 11

项目引入了 不知道哪个版本的 `jswebrtc.js`工具包，在尝试引入其他 npm 包仍然无果后，尝试自行解决问题；

根据报错信息进一步搜索：

![播放失败](data:image/png;base64,)

得到关键信息
- [WebRTC | Failed to execute 'setLocalDescription' on 'RTCPeerConnection': Failed to parse SessionDesc](https://blog.csdn.net/qq_40033374/article/details/87868275)    
- [webrtc-ips](https://github.com/diafygi/webrtc-ips)


#### 言而总之
WebRTC规范仍然在演进，Chrome上目前SDP格式有两种：
- 规范定义的SDP格式（Unified Plan）
- Chrome自己定义的SDP格式（Plan B）

火狐支持前者，如果不指定SDP格式Chrome72默认使用Unified Plan

> ## Controlling Which SDP Format Is Used
### Specifying the sdpSemantics in Your Application
You can override the default behavior by explicitly specifying the sdpSemantics in the RTCPeerConnection constructor, allowing your application to control the SDP format of the client. This flag is Chrome-only; if the browser does not recognize the parameter it is simply ignored.

>// Use Unified Plan or Plan B regardless of what the default browser behavior is.

>new RTCPeerConnection({sdpSemantics:'unified-plan'});

>new RTCPeerConnection({sdpSemantics:'plan-b'});
>
>Unless your application is prepared for both cases, it is recommended that you explicitly set the sdpSemantics to avoid surprises when Chrome’s default behavior changes.

### 关键解决

修改 `jswebrtc.js` 内源码

```
// _self.pc = new RTCPeerConnection(null);

_self.pc = new RTCPeerConnection(
{ iceServers: [{ urls: "stun:stun.l.google.com:19302" }], sdpSemantics: 'plan-b' },
{
		optional: [{ RtpDataChannels: true }]
});
```

### webrtc 视频播放示例

#### html
```
<script src="/assets/sip/jswebrtc.js"></script>
```

```
 <video className="jswebrtc" autoplay controls id="remoteVideo7721" width='100%' height='100%' />
```

```
openUrl = "https://caps.runde.pro/nrtc/v1/play/"
rtcUrl = "webrtc://xxx.xx.xx.xxx/live/xxxxx"

const video = document.getElementById("remoteVideo7721")
player = await new JSWebrtc.Player(
	openUrl,
	rtcUrl,
	{//根据提供的视频案例实现播放
		video: video,
		autoplay: true,
		onPlay: function () {
				console.log('开始播放');
		},
		onFail: function () {
				console.log('播放失败');
		}
	}
);
player.play()
```
